* [[June 14]] &amp;ndash; [[Guadamir]], bishop of [[Roman Catholic Diocese of Vic|Vic]] ([[Spain]])
* [[September 6]] &amp;ndash; [[Liudolf, Duke of Swabia|Liudolf]], duke of [[Duchy of Swabia|Swabia]]
*''date unknown''
